# Git Workflow

- Conventional commits: `feat(frontend):`, `fix(backend):`, `chore:`
- Never commit `.env`, `.env.local`, or credentials
- Do not commit unless explicitly asked
- Keep backend and frontend changes in logical separate commits when possible
- Run `php artisan test` and `npm run build` before marking work complete
